OL,4,CCovid: One-parent rule for boy's cancer
OL,5,Ctreatment 'cruel'
OL,6, A dad who found out his son had
OL,7, leukaemia in a hospital car park said
OL,8, Covid rules banning both parents from
OL,9, going to appointments were "cruel".
OL,11,FNineteen-month-old Carson Josephson
OL,12,Fneeds regular treatment at Noah's Ark
OL,13,FChildren's Hospital, Cardiff.
OL,15,FCovid rules mean only one parent can go
OL,16,Fwith him, with his father Jason having
OL,17,Fto wait outside for hours for news.
OL,19,FCardiff and Vale health board said it
OL,20,Ffollowed Welsh government guidance and
OL,21,Fmade allowances "as appropriate".
